  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为用户更新个人资料和归档账号这两个核心流程画一个旅程图。整体标题我想叫「User Journey: Update Profile or Archive Account」。先从「Profile」区块开始，用户打开个人设置页面，然后查看当前信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section Profile",
        "Open Profile & Settings",
        "View current information"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，「Open Profile & Settings」和「View current information」这两个步骤的评分都是5分对吧？都是用户角色执行的操作。接下来是编辑信息的区块吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open Profile & Settings",
        "View current information",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，评分都是5。接下来是「Edit Information」区块，用户可以修改别名、健身等级和头像，然后保存更改。保存的评分可以降到4，因为有些用户可能会犹豫。保存后系统需要更新状态历史，这个评分是3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Edit Information",
        "Change alias, fitness level, avatar",
        "Save changes",
        "System updates state history"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，「Edit Information」区块已经加上了。现在需要处理账号归档流程，这是第三个区块「Archive Account」对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Edit Information",
        "User",
        "System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，「Archive Account」区块。用户先选择「删除账号」，弹窗确认，评分4。然后系统要执行GDPR合规的删除流程——系统先排队处理删除请求，评分3，最后数据在备份中被匿名化或移除，评分2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Archive Account",
