      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，「Confirm with modal」是用户操作评分4，「System queues GDPR-compliant deletion」和「Data anonymized/removed in backups」都是系统操作，评分分别是3和2。GDPR合规这个点需要体现在标签里吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
